---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import avatar from "@/assets/avatar.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<MainLayout>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
    <div class="text-center pb-8">
      <Image
        src={avatar}
        alt="Sarah Parker"
        class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-8 object-cover"
      />
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 dark:text-white">
        Falconiere Barbosa
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Devoted husband, proud father of √Ågatha, passionate about technology,
        science, music and a lifelong learner.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hello! I'm Falconiere Barbosa, here you will find a collection of my
        thoughts on different topics, from technology to music, from science to
        personal development.
      </p>
      <h2>My Journey</h2>
      <p>
        Since 2014 I've been working as a software developer, and I've been
        learning a lot about technology, software development, and personal
        development. I'm passionate about learning new things and sharing my
        knowledge with others. So, here I am, sharing my thoughts and ideas with
        you.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Technology</li>
        <li>Software Development</li>
        <li>Personal Development</li>
        <li>Music</li>
        <li>Science</li>
        <li>Books</li>
        <li>And much more...</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>My Approach</h2>
      <p>
        I believe in the power of small, intentional changes to create
        meaningful impact. Through my writing, I share practical insights and
        personal experiences to help others navigate their own journey toward a
        more mindful and balanced life.
      </p>

      <blockquote>
        "The key to mindful living isn't in grand gestures, but in the small
        choices we make every day."
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
